latestPosts.caption:
Stress fracture or nail break, both are a nail content creators worst nightmare. 

Stress fracture happens when a blunt trauma creates a crack but the nail is still intact. It can eventually end up in a nail break if you don’t take care of it. 

A nail hardener comes in handy in such situations. It adds a layer of protection allowing the nail to stay intact till it grows out.

I use debelle nail hardener for such scenarios. If you often face brittle nails you can add this hardener to your nail care routine. The best part is that it can be used as is or as a base coat beneath a manicure.

• Nail Primer:
Prep your nails for flawless polish adherence with our Nail Primer. It removes excess oils and residue, ensuring better polish grip and extended wear time.

• Top & Base Coat:
A dual-purpose formula that primes your nails for smooth polish application and seals in color for a long-lasting, chip-resistant finish. Use it as a base to protect your nails and as a top coat to enhance shine and durability.

• Cuticle Oil:
A premium formulation enriched with an ultra-hydrating blend of 6 mythical oils. Specially designed to repair, nourish, and protect dry, damaged cuticles, this cuticle oil provides intense hydration while promoting stronger and healthier nails.
